mlx-lm - https://github.com/ml-explore/mlx-lm

gmlx vendors model/cache classes from unmerged mlx-lm pull requests, with
modifications: gmlx/deepseek_v4_model.py and
gmlx/deepseek_v4_hyper_connection.py from PR #1192 (DeepSeek V4 Flash),
gmlx/minimax_m3_model.py from PR #1401 (MiniMax M3),
gmlx/hy_v3_model.py from PR #1485 (Tencent Hy3), and
gmlx/deepseek_v4_cache.py (PoolingCache/BatchPoolingCache) from PR #1192.
